---
title: Quick Mediterranean Beef, Bacon & Haloumi Burger with Caramelised Onion, Truffle Mayo & Pear Salad
description: We’re so excited about this burger, with crispy chunks of squeaky level-one haloumi, bacon, creamy herby mayo and a side of golden potato wedges. Let’s just say, you won’t need the local pub’s menu on hand when you’ve got this recipe under your belt.
